## Iron Rules
1. Cross-engine: builder engine MUST differ from validator engine
2. Physical lean-kit snapshots only (no symlinks)
3. Project owns its `roadmap.yaml`
4. Inter-team = artifact file (present path to {{OWNER_NAME}} for routing)
5. Every agent needs activation prompt as trigger
6. Team 190 validates at L-GATE_VALIDATE (independent)
7. WP-scoped files go in `_COMMUNICATION/team_[ID]/[WP-ID]/[filename].md`
8. Spoke repos never modify hub governance files directly
9. NEVER write to `_aos/` unless you are Team 00/100/191 under mandate — all other teams use `_COMMUNICATION/team_[ID]/`

